## UI Correctness Criteria

### CRITICAL: Verification Requirements

**After ANY UI change, you MUST verify**:

1. **Visual Verification**: Check http://website.test/ in browser
2. **Layout Integrity**: Confirm layout matches intended design
3. **Responsive Behavior**: Test at mobile, tablet, desktop sizes
4. **No Regressions**: Ensure you didn't break existing functionality
5. **Accessibility**: Verify contrast, focus indicators, semantic HTML

**DO NOT claim success without completing these checks.**

### Contrast Ratios (WCAG AA Required)

**MANDATORY**: All text must meet WCAG AA contrast requirements.

**Minimum Ratios**:
- **Normal text** (< 18pt): ≥ 4.5:1 contrast ratio
- **Large text** (≥ 18pt or 14pt bold): ≥ 3:1 contrast ratio
- **UI components** (buttons, form inputs): ≥ 3:1 against adjacent colors

**Night Sky Palette Ratios** (pre-approved):
- Star White (#ffffff) on Night Black (#000000): 21:1 ✅ Exceeds AA
- Star Yellow (#fff89a) on Night Black (#000000): ~18:1 ✅ Exceeds AA
- Muted Text (rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)) on Night Black: ~14:1 ✅ Exceeds AA

**Custom Colors**:
If using custom colors, verify contrast ratio using:
- WebAIM Contrast Checker: https://webaim.org/resources/contrastchecker/
- Browser DevTools Accessibility panel
- Command: Must pass WCAG AA minimum

**Common Violations to Avoid**:
```css
/* ❌ FAIL: Light gray on white - insufficient contrast */
color: #cccccc;
background: #ffffff;

/* ❌ FAIL: Muted yellow on light background */
color: rgba(255, 248, 154, 0.5);
background: #f0f0f0;

/* ✅ PASS: Star White on Night Black */
color: #ffffff;
background: #000000;

/* ✅ PASS: Star Yellow on Night Black */
color: #fff89a;
background: #000000;
```

### Icon Sizing and Scaling

**CRITICAL**: Icons must scale proportionally with surrounding content.

**Size Guidelines**:
- **Inline icons**: 1.2em - 1.5em (relative to surrounding text)
- **Button icons**: 1em - 1.25em
- **Feature card icons**: 2rem - 3rem (fixed size)
- **Hero icons**: 3rem - 5rem (fixed size)

**Scaling Rules**:
```css
/* ✅ DO: Scale with text */
.icon-inline {
    width: 1.2em;
    height: 1.2em;
