### Card Grid Layout

**CRITICAL**: Card grids must align properly and be responsive.

**Grid Pattern**:
```css
.card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
