```

**Requirements**:
- Cards must have equal heights in grid
- Minimum card width: 300px
- Responsive: 1 column (mobile), 2 columns (tablet), 3 columns (desktop)
- Consistent gap spacing (1.5rem - 2rem)
- Proper alignment within each card

